-- Kabel Deutschland says no break-up fee for Vodafone deal
-- 
-- Mon Jun 24, 2013 5:57am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/24/us-vodafone-kabeldeutschland-breakup-idUSBRE95N0BW20130624

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - Kabel Deutschland said there was no break-up fee included in Vodafone's 7.7 billion euro ($10 billion) takeover deal announced earlier on Monday. 
 The company said there was no break-up fee for both sides of the deal. ($1 = 0.7612 euros) (Reporting by Harro ten Wolde; Editing by  Christoph Steitz )